Class Rock

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elkoserver.server.context.Mod

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, DispatchTarget, Encodable, ContextMod, GeneralMod, ItemMod, ObjectCompletionWatcher, UserMod, Constants, HabitatVerbs

    public class Rock
extends Massive
    Habitat Rock Mod (attached to an Elko Item.) Rock don't really do much. Responds to HELP messages. It *may* be portable based on how Massive it is. Otherwise the client is supposed to be smart and transform interface commands to *other* objects as needed.
    Author:
    randy
